    • readFromFile

      public ArrayList<CurrentPatient> readFromFile(String filename)
      Adds the patients specified by the input file to a list. Assumes a strict file format: (each line) FirstName LastName ABCD-0123 u0123456 2023 05 16 Also assumes there are no duplicate patients in the file.
      Parameters:
      filename - - full or relative path to file containing patient data
